# No Barrel Exports

Do not create barrel files that re-export runtime values from other modules.

Avoid:

```ts
export * from "./process-runner.js";
export { ShellEnvironment } from "./shell-environment.js";
```

Prefer direct imports from the defining module or explicit package subpath exports:

```ts
import { ProcessRunner } from "@winnie/orchestrator/process-runner";
```

Type-only re-exports are allowed when they do not create runtime module graph edges.
